{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Halls that loop forever. You are given tools to break out of the loop but can you truly escape? Hallway shot is what happens when you condense a survival horror game into an extremely long hallway.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Five Halls are randomized with a new hall only replacing an old one when a solution is found. Search through furniture for useful items. Halls will be full of random puzzles, enemies, friends, and a variety of other things. In Hallway Shot you find items, solve puzzles, and escape monsters to solve every hall and eventually leave the hallway. Even if you can't figure out a hall's puzzle, there are numerous alternative solutions that let you remove it from the loop and try to solve it again later.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3326600?t=1738629039","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3326600?t=1738629039","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326600/a699b473e9a2c2452870578e138fd25bbe2f3eec/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738629039","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326600/a699b473e9a2c2452870578e138fd25bbe2f3eec/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738629039","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Halls that loop forever. You are given tools to break out of the loop but can you truly escape? Hallway shot is what happens when you condense a survival horror game into an extremely long hallway.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Five Halls are randomized with a new hall only replacing an old one when a solution is found. Search through furniture for useful items. Halls will be full of random puzzles, enemies, friends, and a variety of other things. In Hallway Shot you find items, solve puzzles, and escape monsters to so